==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Lager beer
<hw>La"ger beer`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr> <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[G.
<ets>lager</ets> bed, storehouse + <ets>bier</ets> beer. See
<er>Lair</er>, and <er>Beer</er>.]</ety> <def>Originally a German beer,
but now also made in immense quantities in the United States; -- so
called from its being laid up or stored for some months before
use.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Lager wine</ent>⟦br⟧
